[b]Players home.

.[b]Entrance[/b] to AARON see picture for info.

I have tested the navmesh with a follower and encountered no problems.

[b]Cleaned[/b] with TES5Edit.[b]
[/b][b]
Requirements[/b]: Dawnguard.Hearthfire.Dragonborn.[b]
[/b][b]
Installation[/b]: Just download with Nexus mod manger, Mod organizer or manual,if you want to install it manually,then you have to extract it into your data file for Skyrim.

[b]Unistallation[/b]:  Just untick in mod manger or mod organzier or delete the files you manually installed.

[b]CREDITS[/b]: Many thanks to "Varlaisaran for his Adabala Building System - Ayleid Transfusion"

My Regards to you all.

Thank You.
